#define mjo_r7_dirsep_str


#define mjo_r7_nil_str

int
mjo_r7_hash(size_t *const, void *const, size_t const, unsigned char const);

INCLUDES

<stddef.h>

DESCRIPTION

Provides symbolic constants for the ASCII character set (0x00-0x7F) and additional utility routines.

Following are commonly used constants defined in the header

mjo_r7_dirsep directory separator constant (character form)
mjo_r7_dirsep_str directory separator constant (string form)
mjo_r7_nil_str nil constant (string form)
mjo_r7_space_str space constant (string form)

“mjo_r7_dirsep” and “mjo_r7_dirsep_str” are platform specific.
